<div class="alone_main_image">
{% image '@AloneBundle/Resources/public/img/GoHomeMain_1.jpg' %}
<img alt="GoHomeMain_1" src="{{ asset_url }}">
{% endimage %}
</div>

<div class="alone_content_left">
	<div class="alone_content">

		<div class="alone_header">
			GoHome
		</div>
		
		<div class="alone_text">
			GoHome is an open world horror game. <br>
			The main character "Thomas" walks home at night after his work in a gas station and feels that something is haunting him.
			<br>
			<br>
			Unaware of his stalkers, he attempts to find out more about them.<br>
			And the more he knows, the more he starts to realize his real, unpleasant situation.
		</div>

	</div>
</div>

<div class="alone_content_right">
	<div class="alone_content">
		
		<div class="alone_header">
		Information
		</div>
		
		<div class="alone_text">
			<li>
				<ul>Release date: ~End of 2020</ul>
			</li>
		</div>		
		
	</div>
</div>	
	
{% endblock %}